---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

export async function serverSideProps() {
  return {
    title: "Guidelines for Campus Placement | TCET Training and Placement Cell",
    description: "Explore the official guidelines for campus placement at Thakur College of Engineering and Technology's Training and Placement Cell. Learn about eligibility criteria, dress code, and essential instructions for a successful placement process."
  };
}

---

<Layout
  title="Guidelines | TCET - Training and Placement Cell"
  description="The official Website of Training and Placement Cell of Thakur College of Engineering and Technology"
>
  <main>
    <section class="block space-y-6 md:space-y-12 w-full lg:px-16">
      <div class="text-gray-900">
        <div class="px-5 py-5 mx-auto">
          <div class="xl:w-11/12 w-full mx-auto">
            <div class="h-full bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border">
              <h1
                class="text-center p-2 text-slate-800 text-xl md:text-3xl xl:text-4xl   font-title font-semibold"
              >
                Guidelines for Campus Placement
              </h1>
              <div
                class="leading-relaxed mb-3 text-justify text-sm md:text-base xl:text-lg text-slate-600 p-2"
              >
                <ul class="list-disc p-1  lg:px-8 2xl:px-12  space-y-2">
                  <li>
                    <p>Refer the T&P Notice Board/College Website every day.</p>
                  </li>

                  <li>
                    <p>
                      Read each line of the notice Carefully and Thoroughly.
                    </p>
                  </li>

                  <li>
                    <p>
                      Only Eligible Students are allowed for placement as per
                      Criteria set by the Companies. If. Any student is found
                      appearing for placement beyond the mentioned criteria, He
                      / she will be eliminated from the placement process.
                    </p>
                  </li>

                  <li>
                    <p>
                      Punctuality during campus placement should be maintained.
                      Students who reach late will not be allowed for the
                      placement process.
                    </p>
                  </li>

                  <li>
                    <p>
                      Students must carry their identity card, an updated copy
                      of resume and photo copy of marks sheets (HSC, SSC,
                      Diploma, All Semesters) in a proper folder.
                    </p>
                  </li>

                  <li>
                    <p>
                      Students should carry their resumes in the format (Soft
                      Copy is Maintained with the placement Cell) provided by
                      the institute. The class representative should submit
                      resumes of all students (of respective Class) in a CD to
                      the placement office.
                    </p>
                  </li>

                  <li>
                    <p>
                      Placement card are maintained by the placement cell.
                      Students must collect their cards one day prior to the
                      placement process and submit them on the same day after
                      the completion of the process.
                    </p>
                  </li>

                  <li>
                    <p>
                      Students must go through the website of the company
                      thoroughly before the placement process.
                    </p>
                  </li>

                  <li>
                    <p>
                      Formal dress is Compulsory, Boys are instructed to wear
                      light color paint shirt, dark color trouser and tie, Girls
                      are instructed to wear either a decent cotton salwar kurta
                      or light color formal Shirt and trouser, Formal Shoes are
                      compulsory, Jeans Sports Shoes are not allowed.
                    </p>
                  </li>

                  <li>
                    <p>
                      The students who registered for a company are expected to
                      appear for the entire recruitment process of the company.
                      If they fail to appear, they will not be considered for
                      the placement further.
                    </p>
                  </li>

                  <li>
                    <p>
                      Dignity and decorum should be maintained throughout the
                      process, especially during the Companyâ€™s Presentation.
                    </p>
                  </li>

                  <li>
                    <p>
                      Parents should be informed about the placement process on
                      the day of the Campus placements, as the process may be
                      extended till late evening.
                    </p>
                  </li>

                  <li>
                    <p>
                      Details must be entered Completely, Correctly and
                      Meticulously on
                    </p>
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <p>
                      Contact T & P Cell for Further
                      Queries:-tcet.tnp@thakureducation.org.
                    </p>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <hr />
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
